AND I'VE CREATED A PRODUCT
THAT HELPS WOMEN

00:20:06,972 --> 00:20:08,841
LOOK AND FEEL FABULOUS.

00:20:08,841 --> 00:20:11,677
MY COMPANY IS MORE THAN
JUST A BUSINESS TO ME.

00:20:11,677 --> 00:20:15,981
IT'S A MESSAGE OF HOPE
THAT ANY DREAM IS POSSIBLE.

00:20:15,981 --> 00:20:19,285
AT 17 YEARS OLD, MY PLANS
FOR THE FUTURE ABRUPTLY ENDED

00:20:19,285 --> 00:20:22,254
BECAUSE I FOUND OUT THAT
I WAS PREGNANT WITH MY SON.

00:20:22,254 --> 00:20:25,925
I GOT MARRIED, 13 MONTHS LATER
I HAD MY DAUGHTER.

00:20:25,925 --> 00:20:28,527
AND THEN
I FOUND MYSELF DIVORCED.

00:20:28,527 --> 00:20:31,864
I BECAME A SINGLE MOM WITH
TWO KIDS TO RAISE ON MY OWN.

00:20:31,864 --> 00:20:34,767
AND I THOUGHT,

00:20:34,767 --> 00:20:37,236
I REFUSE TO LIVE
A LIFE OF MEDIOCRITY,

00:20:37,236 --> 00:20:39,238
AND I REFUSE
TO BE ANOTHER STATISTIC

00:20:39,238 --> 00:20:40,906
OF LIVING OF WELFARE,

00:20:40,906 --> 00:20:43,509
AND I'M JUST
GONNA FIGURE IT OUT.

00:20:43,509 --> 00:20:46,512
AND THEN ONE DAY,
I STUMBLED UPON THIS IDEA

00:20:46,512 --> 00:20:48,514
THAT JUST CAME OUT OF THE BLUE.

00:20:48,514 --> 00:20:50,516
BUT I DIDN'T HAVE
THE MONEY TO START IT.

00:20:50,516 --> 00:20:53,219
SO THEN I THOUGHT,
WHAT ABOUT REAL ESTATE?

00:20:53,219 --> 00:20:55,187
IT TURNS OUT
I WAS REALLY SUCCESSFUL,

00:20:55,187 --> 00:20:59,058
AND I SOLD OVER $9 MILLION
IN REAL ESTATE IN ONE YEAR.

00:20:59,058 --> 00:21:01,293
